songs.title: Do What U Want (Steven Redant Barcelona Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Lady Gaga]
You can't stop my voice 'cause...
Do what you want with my body
Oh
Yeah, yeah
Oh, oh, oh
Oh

[Verse 1: Lady Gaga]
I, I feel good
I walk alone
But then I trip upon myself and I fall
I, I stand up
And then I'm okay
But then you print some shit that makes me wanna scream

[Hook]
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want

[Partial Verse 1]
Print some shit,  print some shit
Print some shit, make me wanna scream
Print some shit,  print some shit
Print some shit, make me wanna scream
Print some shit,  print some shit
Print some shit, make me wanna scream

[Pre-Chorus: Lady Gaga]
So do what you want, what you want with my body
Do what you want, don't stop, let's party
Do what you want, what you want with my body
Do what you want, what you want with my body
Write what you want, say what you want about me
If you're wondering, know that I'm not sorry
Do what you want, what you want with my body
What you want with my body

[Chorus: Lady Gaga]
You can't have my heart and you won't use my mind
But do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body
You can't stop my voice 'cause you don't own my life
But do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body

[Post-Chours: Lady Gaga + Christina Aguilera]
Body, do what you want with my body
Do what you want, do what you want
Hey
My voice, my life, hey
Do what you want with me
Do what you want with my body

[Verse 2: Christina Aguilera]
My bones hurt from all the shows, mmm
But I don't feel the pain, 'cause I'm a pro
I, I sink in
Then I'm okay
'Cause my body belongs to you when I'm on stage, hey

[Interlude: Lady Gaga + (Christina Aguilera)]
Print some shit, print some shit (do what you want)
Print some shit, make me wanna scream
Print some shit, print some shit (do what you want)
Print some shit, make me wanna scream
Print some shit,  print some shit (do what you want)
Print some shit, make me wanna scream
Print some shit,  print some shit (do what you want)
Print some shit, make me wanna scream (scream, scream)

[Pre-Chorus: Lady Gaga]
Do what you want with my body
What you want with my body, boy
What you want with my body

[Chorus: Lady Gaga]
You, you, you, can't have my heart and you won't use my mind
But do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body
You can't stop my voice 'cause you don't own my life
But do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body
You, can't have my heart and you won't use my mind
But do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body
You can't stop my voice 'cause you don't own my life
But do what you want with my body
Do what you want with my body
Do what you want with me
What you want with my body
Do what you want with me
What you want with my body, world
Do what you want with me
What you want with my body
Do what you want with me
What you want with my body, world
Do what you want with my body

[Outro: Lady Gaga]
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want
Do what you, do what you want
Do what you want with my body
Body, body, body....
